name: Dogefather
description: Inspired by Elon Musk’s vision of “The Dogefather,” this meme project blends the iconic themes of The Godfather with the playful and innovative spirit of the Dogecoin community. It’s a humorous tribute to crypto culture, using memes to engage and unite users worldwide. With a nod to cinematic history, we aim to bring laughter and fun into the crypto space, embracing decentralization and community empowerment.
